          .intro-heading WELCOME TO THE BIKE SHARE OF THE FUTURE
          a.btn.btn-xl(href="{{ pathFor 'atSignUp' }}") Sign Up for Free

    //- Explanation Grid Section
    section#explanation.bg-light-gray
      .container
        .row.wow.bounceInUp.animated(data-wow-delay="0.1s")
          .col-lg-12.text-center
            h2.section-heading What is a bikeshare?
            h3.section-subheading.text-muted Bike renting has never been this easy
        .row.wow.slideInLeft.animated(data-wow-delay="0.75s" style="visibility: visible; -webkit-animation-delay: 0.5s;")
          .col-sm-3.col-sm-offset-2
            .team-member
              img.img-responsive.img-circle(src='img/about/explanation/1.png' alt='')
          .col-sm-5
            .explanation-text
              h5 &nbsp;
              h3 Find a Bike
              p Using the online map of each bike, find the nearest available bike.
        .row.wow.slideInRight.animated(data-wow-delay="1.25s" style="visibility: visible; -webkit-animation-delay: 0.5s;")
          .col-sm-3.visible-xs-block
            .team-member
              img.img-responsive.img-circle(src='img/about/explanation/2.png' alt='')
          .col-sm-5.col-sm-offset-2
            .explanation-text
              h5 &nbsp;
              h3 Unlock
              p Using your Red Bars ID, swipe it by the lock pad and the bike will instantly unlock. Twist the lock into the riding position and you are ready to go.
          .col-sm-3.hidden-xs
            .team-member
              img.img-responsive.img-circle(src='img/about/explanation/2.png' alt='')
        .row.wow.slideInLeft.animated(data-wow-delay="1.75s" style="visibility: visible; -webkit-animation-delay: 0.5s;")
          .col-sm-3.col-sm-offset-2
