              img.img-responsive.img-circle(src='img/about/explanation/3.png' alt='')
          .col-sm-5
            .explanation-text
              h5 &nbsp;
              h3 Return
              p This is the best part, when you are done, return the bike to any bike rack on campus. We won't limit you to just a handful of stations.
